Cara membuat virtual environment di python:

1. Buat folder project
syntax: mkdir [nama_projectmu]
$ mkdir flappy_bird

2. Masuk ke folder project di visualstudio code
syntax: code [nama_projectmu]
$ code flappy_bird

--- Didalam vscode lakukan ini (menggunakan terminal divscode):
3. Masuk folder project
syntax: cd [nama_projectmu]
$ cd flappy_bird

4. Bikin python virtual environment di dalam projectmu
syntax: python3 -m venv [nama_environmentmu]
/flappybird$ python3 -m venv myFlappyBird

5. Activasi environment nya
/flappybird$ source myFlappyBird/bin/activate

Ini buat deactivasi environment nya
/flappybird$ deactivate
